{"tid":942124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天降橫財：執錢使用是否違法？　蔣麗芸促警交代","createTime":"2018-12-15T12:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T17:19:27.000Z","uid":88743,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd26c97c97a1c750df5a3da146263dc424d0e916","tid":942124,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:01:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>天降橫財：執錢使用是否違法？　蔣麗芸促警交代</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181215/bkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028834767a5895d0167b0f59b6d06a4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181215%2Fbkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dhk_news%26eventid%3D4028834767a5895d0167b0f59b6d06a4&d=%2FiaVEXIQqIBypw03stmNOpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c99c98bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181215/bkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001.html?eventsection=hk_news&amp;eventid=4028834767a5895d0167b0f59b6d06a4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181215/photo/bkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181215173546\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181215173546&h=023a26da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔣麗芸認為，撒錢行為引起市民瘋狂爭搶，產生混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181215/photo/bkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001_02p.jpg?20181215173546\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20181215173546&h=5a248ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員到深水埗調查。(黃偉邦攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181215/photo/bkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001_03p.jpg?20181215173546\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20181215173546&h=db01ead5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冷氣機及外牆仍留有鈔票(圓圈示)。(黃偉邦攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181215/photo/bkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001_04p.jpg?20181215173546\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181215165852500-1215_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20181215173546&h=ea19dda2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員檢走鈔票。(黃偉邦攝)<br />\n<br />\n深水埗今日(15日)有人將大疊100港元鈔票從天台撒下，途人瘋狂執錢。民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸認為，因有關行為引起市民瘋狂爭搶，雖無人受傷，但已產生混亂，她要求警方跟進及調查有關金錢是否合法所得，而市民使用有關金錢是否違法，警方有需要交代。<br />\n<br />\n今次撒錢期間，有途人在地上執起一張100港元鈔票，警員見狀，即時上前阻止並登記其資料，並取有關鈔票調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員喎 制定法律既人竟然唔識解釋法律 要問警察?<br />\n點解可以咁柒 唔識仲要咁高調 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b544d998f83d0b9d767157ba993a40ac7b1d5542","tid":942124,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de46c85d286a3c14bcb2727653ae43c5c16217bd","tid":942124,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:09:15.000Z","msg":"真係好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647f6d02f4000a185c3b15355e529f90e760abf6","tid":942124,"uid":124410,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"錢多派比人有乜犯法？<br />\n好過你個仆街政府大把錢都唔派明人起埋啲垃圾高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dff79c4926256c5d1b6c976297d12a379ced53","tid":942124,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"647f6d02f4000a185c3b15355e529f90e760abf6","tid":942124,"uid":124410,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"錢多派比人有乜犯法？<br />\n好過你個仆街政府大把錢都唔派明人起埋啲垃圾高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:14:23.000Z","msg":"以派錢形式意圖引起公眾混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469b9f7b8742247b6b5691ed0a6de1058f20487d","tid":942124,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:32:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e68be383ed3fb9811d572d25dd31b509bc5d05c","tid":942124,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"係喎，佢係立法會議員，仲要問返人係曝露自己無知"},{"pid":"dac8b07b960d70da16702cd8d66d3ef915f37e2c","tid":942124,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e68be383ed3fb9811d572d25dd31b509bc5d05c","tid":942124,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"係喎，佢係立法會議員，仲要問返人係曝露自己無知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"係囉 立法會做立法工作<br />\n做立法工作既人 問返人轉頭咁樣算唔算違法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n立圾會已經夠垃圾 佢係垃圾之中既垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be83c84810941f9432af37f88373b3cc8e5d7b62","tid":942124,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"根本就自暴其短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"